# NovaFin Data Dictionary

This document describes the synthetic datasets used in the NovaFin Analytics Platform.

All data is fictional and generated for portfolio purposes.

## Tables

- `dim_customers`: Customer attributes and acquisition information
- `fact_funnel`: Customer funnel progression from visitor to activation
- `fact_subscriptions`: Monthly subscription and add-on revenue
- `fact_engagement`: Monthly product engagement behavior
- `fact_utilization`: Monthly feature utilization
- `fact_retention`: Monthly active, churn, and reactivation status
- `fact_forecast_inputs`: Forecasting and scenario planning assumptions
- `fact_budget`: Budget and plan targets for actual-vs-budget analysis